item.title: Robot Contest
item.description: Participated to NHK Student Robot Contest (NHK学生ロボコン) from U-Tokyo team, RoboTech. I was mostly resposible for mechanical design and entire team manegement. Not only I design the robot, but also I estabilish RoboTech fund to support my team from financial aspect.
